      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Outgoing longwave radiation during the night will be quite good over a wide area. The surface of the snowpack will freeze to form a strong crust. The weather conditions as the day progresses will give rise to softening of the snowpack, in particular at low and intermediate altitudes. <br/> Weak layers exist in the snowpack in particular on shady slopes."
